AUDIO: 'By the end of this video, you\'ll know exactly how to put a face like mine on your own agent, and the full plugin guide is in the LiveKit docs. Linked in the description. For anyone new here, what am I actually looking at? You\'re looking at a single reference'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'image brought to life. Runway Characters generates me as a real-time intelligent avatar from one photo, no fine-tuning required. The lip sync, the eye movement, the'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
